nodes.text: Greg Ellis (born March 21, 1968) is an English screen and voice actor. He provided the voice for Mical in Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords. He also voices Turk Falso in Star Wars: The Clone Wars and Valen Rudor in Star Wars Rebels.
